007_facility_dm This map was originally created by Semedi for Goldeneye Source. All credit goes to him and Rareware for originally designing this level in the first place. This DM Version has: - A Nav File - Spawn Text File - A Radar Map - Cubemaps Put the 007_facility_dm.bsp into cstrike/maps and put 007_facility_dm.txt into cstrike/cfg/cssdm/spawns to install the map. Note: This map was made for Death Match, nothing else. The default CT spawn area doesn't even have a buy zone, because you wouldn't need one in Death Match so don't complain about things like that. If you have any other questions or comments though, please let me know.

Quick Tutorial

*Press E above the windows to close them up.
*Break the small boxes on the sides to get more weapons.
*Break the door on top of the ladder to get to roof.
*Press E on the Explosive box to get a HE. (Theres more then one)
*Don't Die!
 
FAQ

Have Fun!

ZM_Swathouses

Version No. 1

This is the first map I ever made. Please don't complain that I suck :] Hopefully this map is good enough to get onto an Official Zombie Mod Server :D

The next version (update) I will clean up the textures, such as adding grass, dirt, etc. and making the water more clearer and realistic. Also, I will also be making a button for the elevator so you don't have to wait for the elevator everytime someone goes up to it.

Water Problems (Secret Area) Help -
I know that sometimes you can't get out of the water; I added an invisible go-thru texture on the top of it so the water looks nicer when you swim in it.

The solution is to press "SPACEBAR" to get out. To get on the boxes, Hold "W" and keep pressing "CTRL" (Crouch) until you get on one. I will take the invisible go-thru textures off next version.

GG_X_RUSH_V2 AND X_RUSH_V2
by dustandechoes89

V2 Notes
=====================================================================
Added a skybox, and a few small touchups to the map itsself, including a fix on the 
ceiling in the covered bridge, and scooted a few boxes. The pack still contains a 
gungame version of the map.
=====================================================================

Original Notes
=====================================================================
X_rush is a fairly large map with many hidden weapons. There is a scout on top 
of the covered bridge, smoke and HE grenades on the cornered balconies, an m4 in the 
T-spawn vent, and an AK in the CT-spawn vent. To retrieve the vent weapons, simply
buy a nade, and toss it in the vent (it works best if you hit the very top of the slanted
piece). Have fun!
=====================================================================
The only difference between the maps is the "gg" map (Gungame, of course) 
has the buyzones and weapons taken out, as well as the vent.
=====================================================================
Feel free to send comments and/or suggestions to arekuthelastspartan@hotmail.com
